{"tid":1253002,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有古怪既機票網","createTime":"2019-06-23T10:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T06:32:21.000Z","uid":254854,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"21ba9ea7e460427bc3b3f9fc19a3f5ef96efcafb","tid":1253002,"uid":254854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:28:17.000Z","msg":"事源今朝係Skyscanner搵左張去日本機票，<a href=\"http://咁就係間叫kiwi.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%92%81%E5%B0%B1%E4%BF%82%E9%96%93%E5%8F%ABkiwi.com&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=e62159d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">咁就係間叫kiwi.com</a>既網買左張飛。<br />\n<br />\n點知下晝佢出email,話係航空公司個邊要求加多$2000幾先可以留張飛。<br />\n<br />\n我真係睇唔透，係可以咁樣坐地起價架咩？<br />\n<br />\n一黎都有少少係我自己無search間網既可靠性，所以呢個post係提醒大家千奇唔好用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"http://kiwi.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkiwi.com&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=3ad5f38e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">kiwi.com</a><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\"></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n下附要求加價既email圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mBcszbB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmBcszbB.jpg&h=73029ca3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\np.s.已要求退款"},{"pid":"f95a8e91a12cee5c6cbdf3ca3bc4090aedaf798c","tid":1253002,"uid":68728,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"財到光棍手 咁易比你退款?"},{"pid":"9301dc50b9cd8925099fa14e035af54fd90678b3","tid":1253002,"uid":254854,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f95a8e91a12cee5c6cbdf3ca3bc4090aedaf798c","tid":1253002,"uid":68728,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"財到光棍手 咁易比你退款?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:36:12.000Z","msg":"希望在明天<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea35394b51abaafea83313f33545ebbf0d38dd0","tid":1253002,"uid":72608,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:31:50.000Z","msg":"下次小心D"},{"pid":"0c7cc21a5a89ec86f249b2879166c68bac143316","tid":1253002,"uid":230198,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:34:55.000Z","msg":"樓主買個教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw, 點解當初揀呢間, 平其他好多咩?"},{"pid":"a704214e7fcc5fb8a83f4372dd7e72693fabb1b2","tid":1253002,"uid":102606,"like":29,"dislike":4,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:38:17.000Z","msg":"一路都唔明點解有人會為咗慳少少錢都唔直接喺official site買機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292aaa3e3249f9044e984e961678a78d61b43ad7","tid":1253002,"uid":72725,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:41:51.000Z","msg":"壹仔翻查資料，原來來自中國內地的攜程旅行網（CTrip），早於2010年2月以6.84億港元購入90%永安股權，隨後2016年11月，以135億港元收購Skyscanner，<a href=\"http://一年後再收購來自美國的Trip.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84Trip.com&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=4d388af9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">一年後再收購來自美國的Trip.com</a>。<a href=\"http://至於Kiwi.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%87%B3%E6%96%BCKiwi.com&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=2602f4e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">至於Kiwi.com</a>，就是以攜程作第二大股東的同程藝龍，於2018年簽訂的戰略合作伙伴。簡單來說，<a href=\"http://無論你是選擇Trip.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%84%A1%E8%AB%96%E4%BD%A0%E6%98%AF%E9%81%B8%E6%93%87Trip.com&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=e9905766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">無論你是選擇Trip.com</a>、永安、<a href=\"http://還是Kiwi.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%82%84%E6%98%AFKiwi.com&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=d336bfea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">還是Kiwi.com</a>，也是攜程集團旗下品牌。難怪Skyscanner瘋狂推介自己人，原來全部來自同一集團。換言之，所謂「綜合多間OTA價格優惠」，其實只是「自己平過自己」的技倆罷了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20190114/2_649349_0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190114%2F2_649349_0%2F&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=27436aa4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190114%2F2_649349_0%2F&h=845355da\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20190114/2_649349_0/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4175397ff23c9d13bd488b15ed67d6c679cca9f7","tid":1253002,"uid":247454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:52:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7bcb7594c2395de1dd358ce6ff8473b19f74e09f","tid":1253002,"uid":31261,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:56:47.000Z","msg":"kiwi慣犯黎 試過俾佢起價<br />\n要求退款啦 要等多幾日但會退的"},{"pid":"47341661aa73fdd6cf22ceeb35e771bc7509fe6d","tid":1253002,"uid":6845,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:58:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前買兩次無事 睇黎死好彩<br />\n<br />\n（係平幾多下）"},{"pid":"16d64d4f65b0d9cf75d2bb1fcb37048862218e7f","tid":1253002,"uid":5339,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:58:28.000Z","msg":"用hutchgo好啲 長和旗下"},{"pid":"9d6993f28b218fcdcc6dda8cb84e05725a8ce9ba","tid":1253002,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:05:57.000Z","msg":"有無 比較過其他機票網站 加完假之後係咪一樣價錢"},{"pid":"a8898ade4cd58996a35a72203c5136fbad6d6edd","tid":1253002,"uid":254854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c7cc21a5a89ec86f249b28